From: Marti Maria <marti.maria@littlecms.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Nov 2023 09:22:33 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Another check to cgats

Again, pointless but for fuzzer hapiness.
---
 src/cmscgats.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/cmscgats.c b/src/cmscgats.c
index edf4c9eb..6e93bb62 100644
--- a/src/cmscgats.c
+++ b/src/cmscgats.c
@@ -1671,7 +1671,7 @@ char* GetData(cmsIT8* it8, int nSet, int nField)
     int nSamples    = t -> nSamples;
     int nPatches    = t -> nPatches;
 
-    if (nSet >= nPatches || nField >= nSamples)
+    if (nSet < 0 || nSet >= nPatches || nField < 0 || nField >= nSamples)
         return NULL;
 
     if (!t->Data) return NULL;
